Moreno, 1889:29
</taxonomicName>
; Moreno &amp; Mercerat, 1891; Brodkorb, 1967 (syn. of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Brodkorb" authorityYear="1967" box="[151,369,1822,1846]" class="Aves" family="Phorusrhacidae" genus="Prophororhacos" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gruiformes" pageId="31" pageNumber="86" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="australis">
